00:00:59.606 --> 00:01:01.480
I'll write that as a
hundredths place just so

00:01:01.480 --> 00:01:03.170
that we can keep track of it.

00:01:03.170 --> 00:01:07.170
And then finally,
we have 7/1000,

00:01:07.170 --> 00:01:09.740
that's the 1000th place.

00:01:09.740 --> 00:01:14.100
So we could write
that, plus 7/1000.

00:01:14.100 --> 00:01:16.060
So if we would write
down everything

00:01:16.060 --> 00:01:18.710
