only way to say this.

00:01:49.880 --> 00:01:52.320
Another way of
thinking about it is

00:01:52.320 --> 00:01:56.690
to try to merge the 5/10 and the
7/1000 in terms of thousandths.

00:01:56.690 --> 00:01:57.890
So let's think about this.

00:01:57.890 --> 00:02:00.380
So we could write this
as-- so once again, we

00:02:00.380 --> 00:02:03.590
