00:02:12.580 --> 00:02:14.990
So then we will
have-- so this 5/10

00:02:14.990 --> 00:02:20.930
is the same thing
as 500 over 1,000.

00:02:20.930 --> 00:02:25.900
And the 7/1000 is still 7/1000.

00:02:25.900 --> 00:02:32.150
And these two
combined are 507/1000.

00:02:32.150 --> 00:02:37.560
So we could just call
this 20,000 and 507/1000.

00:02:37.560 --> 00:02:39.450
so let's write that down.

00:02:39.450 --> 00:03:06.140
So we could just say this
is 20,000 and 507/1000.

00:03:06.140 --> 00:03:11.000
This is 1/1000, while this right
